Comments: From cities rich in greenery to those with stunning architecture to those that boast incredible beaches, there are beautiful places all across the 50 states. To find the most picturesque locales around the US, INSIDER consulted polls by travel publications and research conducted by real estate groups and tourism advisors. In no particular order, these are 21 of the prettiest cities in the country.

Classic. It's a word that has so many meanings. Rooted in tradition. Built around etiquette. Ceremony. Simplicity. Having written about and been a part of the wedding industry for the better part of 15 years though, the word classic has assumed a far different, far more broad intention than ever before. We feature whimsical, personality infused "classic" weddings all the time with the true definition simply tucked into the culture and ceremony that the wedding is inspired by.
